bioghist.p:
On December 29, 1870, married Mary Relief Niles, 1839-1916, daughter of John Barron
                Niles. Children: Mary Polke, 1871-1873; Emmet, 1873-1937; Margaret, 1875-1884;
                Fanny, 1877-1979; Sarah Polke, 1880-1885; Katherine, 1881-1888.

arrangement.p:
The collection is organized into the following series: I. Biographical/Genealogical;
                II. Correspondence; III. Diaries; IV. Photographs; V. Letter copy books; VI.
                Business/Financial; VII. Printed; and, VIII. Miscellaneous.
